verbose_text: Cell culture studies showed that the treatment with TWEAK increases the expression of muscle specific E3 ubiquitin ligases MuRF1 and MAFbx and stimulates the conjugation of ubiquitin with MyHC in C2C12 myotubes suggesting that TWEAK causes degradation of MyHC through the activation of UPS [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: ubiquitin ligases MuRF1 and MAFbx and stimulates the conjugation of ubiquitin
